thread.title: Liberty Leaflets in Amritsar

author: tribuneindia.com
title: Liberty Leaflets in Amritsar
text: IT is stated that lately Liberty leaflets were found scattered in the classrooms of the P.B.N. High School. It appears some time before the classes meet, the rooms are ordinarily kept open to allow plenty of fresh air into them. As the classes met on Friday, the 8th instant, these leaflets were discovered on the desks of the students in the various classrooms. The Manager promptly collected all the copies, 11 in number, and handed them over to the Police. No clue has yet been found of the culprit who distributed the leaflets.
